nodes.bodyText:
@thadguidry Your proposed test would fail. The result would actually be z--c-a which is one of the weirdly inconsistent things about this.
For the record, I wasn't actually considering any unrelated changes to join() as part of this PR. I was just flagging the inconsistency for future review.
I added the tests because I was working in the neighborhood of completely untested functions. I added the comments when I had to change the tests to match the inconsistent behavior of our current implementation.

